overview: Hulk Hogan squares off against Vader for the WCW World Heavyweight Championship. Sting & "The Macho Man" Randy Savage battle Avalanche & Big Bubba Rogers. Harlem Heat faces The Nasty Boys for the WCW World Tag Team Championship on the line and much more!
tagline: The Biggest Brawl Of Them All
title: WCW SuperBrawl V
